::Zardus::

Zardus' comp beeps as he enters the bridge of the Alliance base, reporting a 
transmission from the Millitron ship. He frowns for a sec, tapping a key to 
send a reply.

"Iron Fist, this is Zardus," the transmission read, "What is it you're 
contacting me about?"
